02:17:41.760 --> 02:17:42.760
[Guest]: How has it changed?

02:17:42.760 --> 02:17:50.760
[Guest]: The logic of the house we used to live in together was that there were all freshers.

02:17:50.760 --> 02:17:51.760
[Guest]: Right.

02:17:51.760 --> 02:17:52.760
[Guest]: You ask,

02:17:52.760 --> 02:17:54.760
[Guest]: you invite a fresher to work with you.

02:17:54.760 --> 02:17:55.760
[Guest]: Mostly,

02:17:55.760 --> 02:17:57.760
[Guest]: some people were from Indore,

02:17:57.760 --> 02:17:59.760
[Guest]: but we would hire from everywhere.

02:17:59.760 --> 02:18:00.760
[Guest]: Right.

02:18:00.760 --> 02:18:01.760
[Guest]: So people would come from small,

02:18:01.760 --> 02:18:02.760
[Guest]: small towns.

02:18:02.760 --> 02:18:05.760
[Guest]: The biggest headache of their life is finding a house.

02:18:05.760 --> 02:18:07.760
[Guest]: No one gives a good house to bachelors.

02:18:07.760 --> 02:18:08.760
[Guest]: Even if you give it,

02:18:08.760 --> 02:18:10.760
[Guest]: there are 50 types of problems in it.

02:18:10.760 --> 02:18:13.760
[Guest]: So the lowest type of property in the city is given to bachelors.

02:18:13.760 --> 02:18:15.760
[Guest]: They don't give good properties to bachelors.

02:18:15.760 --> 02:18:16.760
[Guest]: Then after that,

02:18:16.760 --> 02:18:17.760
[Guest]: even if they get it,

02:18:17.760 --> 02:18:19.760
[Guest]: find a maid for cleaning.

02:18:19.760 --> 02:18:21.760
[Guest]: Who will cook food?

02:18:21.760 --> 02:18:22.760
[Guest]: If you put a tiffin outside,

02:18:22.760 --> 02:18:24.760
[Guest]: half the time you will sleep hungry.

02:18:24.760 --> 02:18:26.760
[Guest]: If you put a maid at home,

02:18:26.760 --> 02:18:27.760
[Guest]: if you put a cook,

02:18:27.760 --> 02:18:28.760
[Guest]: then that too,

02:18:28.760 --> 02:18:30.760
[Guest]: there are thousands of problems.

02:18:30.760 --> 02:18:31.760
[Guest]: Then grocery shopping,

02:18:31.760 --> 02:18:32.760
[Guest]: all that.

02:18:32.760 --> 02:18:33.760
[Guest]: Right.

02:18:33.760 --> 02:18:38.760
[Guest]: So our thought was that we have invited them to do a job.

02:18:38.760 --> 02:18:42.760
[Guest]: Why can't we solve everything else for them and just let them do the job?

02:18:42.760 --> 02:18:43.760
[Guest]: Right.

02:18:43.760 --> 02:18:44.760
[Guest]: So basically,

02:18:44.760 --> 02:18:46.760
[Guest]: we gave them a pre-made solution.

02:18:46.760 --> 02:18:47.760
[Guest]: This is a house.

02:18:47.760 --> 02:18:49.760
[Guest]: You go and live here.

02:18:49.760 --> 02:18:50.760
[Guest]: There is a cook here.

02:18:50.760 --> 02:18:52.760
[Guest]: He will cook food in the morning and evening.

02:18:52.760 --> 02:18:54.760
[Guest]: Someone else is responsible for its grocery shopping.

02:18:54.760 --> 02:18:56.760
[Guest]: Your job is just to work.

02:18:56.760 --> 02:18:59.760
[Guest]: You don't have to worry about anything else.

02:18:59.760 --> 02:19:00.760
[Guest]: And you can live a,

02:19:00.760 --> 02:19:01.760
[Guest]: like a nice life,

02:19:01.760 --> 02:19:02.760
[Guest]: better life,

02:19:02.760 --> 02:19:03.760
[Guest]: basically,

02:19:03.760 --> 02:19:05.760
[Guest]: than you would otherwise live as a bachelor,

02:19:05.760 --> 02:19:06.760
[Guest]: etc.

02:19:06.760 --> 02:19:07.760
[Guest]: And it worked.

02:19:07.760 --> 02:19:09.760
[Guest]: We used to love the fact that they didn't have to take a headache.

02:19:09.760 --> 02:19:10.760
[Guest]: And the productivity was high.

02:19:10.760 --> 02:19:12.760
[Guest]: The food was good.

